values: Maybe i shouldn't have come i don't know. but i'm here. and of course everything goes wrong. just one thing after another. should have expected it i guess. just how my life works. my mom thinks i'm some whore and thinks i killed her grandbaby even though i've never been pregnant. i just want everything to go away. my parents hate me. i could go back to washington but i'd just be homeless again but at least i'd have more friends. i don't exactly have a place here either so not sure how it's much better. could go up to another state but then i'll just be living off someone else till something does work out. could go to yet another state but then i'll just be again living off someone and i don't know. i just want to vanish again. i don't get it how nothing ever works out. could have something set up months in advance and it still wont work out. why is this world so against me? why can't i change things? why can't i change myself even? I guess this is hell. Maybe that's it. I'm just living in hell right now. maybe i already died and this is just what i get. *sighs*

You know i woke up that morning and everything started going to chaos. then all was quiet. the bus ride to school silent, the classes in school full of questioning kids trying to figure out the truth and what was going on. everything stopped. Flags went up, everyone came together. All thinking terrorists. 

What if it wasn't terrorists? what if it was all a big lie and the government was the one that kill over 3000 people that day, not to mention the people that are still sick, and dieing from the abspestas (however you spell that). Why wont people ask questions? why are people in fear? Why isn't anyone doing anything to find answers. and why aren't we getting answers. Why is everything that relates to 9-11 deleted. Why is all the evidence vanishing about 9-11, what have they got to hide? what happened to freedom of information, and speech? the right to know? why is no one educated anymore?! 

Those two towers did not come down from the planes but there is undenyable proof that they came down because they were brought down on purpose. Controlled demolition. The pane that supposively hit the pentagon and shanksville were not planes at all. there were no signs of there being a plane. No wrekage nothing. the hole in the pentagon was to small for a plane of the magnitude. not to mention a plane would not have made it all the way through the pentagon... Ask the questions, demand the answers. do something about it.

and yeah apparently... everything that happened everyone already knows around snohomish go figure. I just hate to know what rumors are going around and what people are actually saying and what bs is being said. i know how people are. one of my old friends didn't sound to happy... *Whimpers* shit. 
but yeah my parents, are kinda more relaxed.. kinda... i know they are talking behind my back and such things. *stares at joel who's playing halo right now* 
the only time i can get online or even talk to people is when i'm with him. my parents wont let me do anything but email or apply for jobs. which well yeah. not exactly happy about it. but i have a roof over my head i guess. though they are threatening to kick me out. i kinda hate them right now. at least they are letting me out finally to get a job with out bitching constantly. 
I don't know what it is about Joel. it's like we end up argueing or whatever but then we work things out. We always talk, and work everything out, and it's cool. He tells me how much he loves me and how he hasn't felt like this before. We both have our problems to work out, and he's trying to do his best and working on his problems and helping me to get on my feet. he makes me smile. i keep questioning whether he is better than justin or not. i keep asking myself about so many things. i'm not even sure of what to do right now. Justin and i never argued really. but then we didn't grow much either. I don't think i felt anything more for him then when we first started honestly. Joel and i have had our ups and downs, but our love is growing for each other. rar. thinking to much. questioning to much. *Sighs*


and yes i do have a myspace and yes i actually check it more often now

i gave in and lost him. now they hate me. Not justin, just his family. his mom already did hate me. yesterday was a disaster. i lost my fiance. i gave him up. it really wasn't fair to him anyways, i didn't love him like i used to. really fucking hurt right now. and so is he. i hurt cause i hurt him. i hate hurting people.
My friend joel, he's amazing. he's been at my side the whole time. holding my hand comforting me. wanting to take my pain away from me, wanting to take my tears and cry for me. i don't know what to do.

~Moonlight Shadow~
The last that ever she saw him,
Carried away by a moonlight shadow.
He passed on worried and warning,
Carried away by a moonlight shadow.
Lost in a riddle that Saturday night,
Far away on the other side.
He was caught in the middle of a desperate fight
And she couldn't find how to push through.

The trees that whisper in the evening,
Carried away by a moonlight shadow.
Sing a song of sorrow and grieving,
Carried away by a moonlight shadow.
All she saw was a silhouette of a gun,
Far away on the other side.
He was shot six times by a man on the run
And she couldn't find how to push through.

[ Chorus ]

I stay, I pray
See you in heaven far away.
I stay, I pray
See you in heaven one day.

Four a.m. in the morning,
Carried away by a moonlight shadow.
I watched your vision forming,
Carried away by a moonlight shadow.
Stars roll slowly in a silvery night,
Far away on the other side.
Will you come to terms with me this night,
But she couldn't find how to push through.

[ Repeat Chorus ]

Far away on the other side.

Caught in the middle of a hundred and five.
The night was heavy and the air was alive,
But she couldn't find how to push through.

Carried away by a moonlight shadow.
Carried away by a moonlight shadow.
Far away on the other side.
But she couldn't find how to push through.

Storybook Love

by Willy DeVille

Come my love, I'll tell you a tale
of a boy and girl, and their love story,
and how he loved her oh, so much,
and all the charms she did possess.

Now this did happen once upon a time
When things were not so complex,
And how he worshipped the ground she walked.
When he looked in her eyes, he became obsessed.

CHORUS:
My love is like a storybook story.
But it's as real as the feelings I feel.
My love is like a storybook story.
But it's as real as the feelings I feel;
it's as real as the feelings I feel.

A prince could have within his keeping;
His spells to weave and steal a heart
Within her breast, but only sleeping.

sitting at isaac's house waiting for him to come back... *sighs*


i hate being alone in a room, cause then i think... to much. about the past about him, whether he's changed or not, whether the past is still looming.. fuck the past. we'll see what happens... 

still need to talk to him.... everytime i'm here something else comes up... damnit.

i have to talk to him and work things out...

tell him what i really think

tell him what i truly feel

and how i know i shouldn't have allowed what i had, and.... ugh.. so fast, so short time, so many times....

*takes deep breath* i love him. 

i just hope he actually does love me back. (i know deep down he does, but sometimes...)

he's brilliant, mature, gentle, funny....
yet something there underneath that bothers me that makes me long to know him more, and figure him out.. what is there and why

for so long i got used to things changeing so much that i began to relize that you can't really trust anything anyone.. not fully. i want to trust him. but how? 
one week i'd be good friends with someone then the next everything falling apart. so many groups fell apart, so many friends that like each other hate each other now. 

i just pray things are different now. 

I watch him work, and fiddle with technology, and i admire his beauty, his gentle face and touch, careful delibrate movements, his eyes so deep, he's just so different. so ... i dont' know how to explain it. 

maybe i just don't know what to do or say.

yet at times i wonder, i wonder if it's real, i wonder if things have indeed changed. 
I know he'll disappear one day for a long time, and all i can do is wait. but can i? should i? 
will he want me still?
I fear i wont recognize him when he comes back, i fear that he will change and be someone completely different. 

maybe this makes no sense to anyone else, maybe it's just me. so many times i've been told i'll just get hurt again. will i?

if only i knew half of his thoughts about me... what he really thinks... 

or should i know?


wtf is wrong with me? meh long post... thinking to much again. i guess things will all work themselves out in time. and talk to him in a few days. 
i see him to much... way to much, yet it's kinda a get away, a place i can relax... meh... i should just probably not go over there during the week... i dont know... *sighs* i wish i knew what he truly wants. 




*Shrugs* life goes on day by day. at least work has been good. cept i get four days off... randomly and not the day i asked for off... rar.

woot more money to be spent for college. what fun. 
i miss you all. *hugs to everyone*
